{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"975820620c","title":"关于华东沿海构筑工事问题致陈毅电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1ebdd3aa05","index":0,"year":1951,"month":1,"day":29,"articleId":"975820620c"}],"tags":[{"id":"1feb996ca7","name":"陈毅","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"a80893a10c","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"975820620c","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陈毅，当时任中国人民解放军华东军区司令员。"},{"id":"0549d014bf","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"975820620c","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"饶，指饶激石，当时任中国人民解放军华东军区政治委员。"}],"contents":[{"id":"c885d28a43","type":"title","text":"关于华东沿海构筑工事问题致陈毅\"电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"975820620c"},{"id":"a80893a10c","type":"paragraph","text":"陈毅同志，并告饶及中南军区，广东军区，广西军区，华东军区：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"975820620c"},{"id":"0549d014bf","type":"paragraph","text":"鉴于广东方面过去时期未经中南军区勘察指导设计，到处做工事，结果无用，浪费极大，此次华东在厦门、平潭、舟山、吴淞四处修筑要寒或工事，在福建修南平同安公路，务请你们注意事先给以指导。第一，不要在指定地区不经研究设计随便修建，以致无用浪费；第二，在指定地区内亦只择最需要者做，不要到处做；第三，大陆海岸线及内地根本不要做；第四，大陆兵力，位于纵深地区，敌来应让其登陆然后相机击之，不要到处防守，不要阻其登陆；第五，建筑材料，必要者不可客惜，照需要支给，但仍须防止浪费，注意废物利用，注意节省","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"975820620c"},{"id":"81503babec","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"975820620c"},{"id":"79ef1e1a2f","type":"paragraph","text":"一月廿九日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"975820620c"}],"page":{"id":"c0326a7fc5","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"975820620c","start":87,"end":87}}}},"__N_SSG":true}